From: Andre Klapper <a9016009@gmx.de>
Date: Fri, 6 Mar 2026 18:02:53 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 44/50] Remove pep8 standalone Python linter

Summary:
pep8 saw its last standalone release in 2017 per https://pypi.org/project/pep8/#changelog. People should migrate to pycodestyle for it.

Refs T16542

Test Plan: Run `../arcanist/bin/arc linters`, see that `pep8 (Python PEP 8)` is not listed anymore.

Reviewers: O1 Blessed Committers, mainframe98

Reviewed By: O1 Blessed Committers, mainframe98

Subscribers: mainframe98, tobiaswiese, valerio.bozzolan, Matthew, Cigaryno

Maniphest Tasks: T16542

Differential Revision: https://we.phorge.it/D26826
